item.dc:creator: @xx_matty_xx Justin Bieber
item.description:
@xx_matty_xx wrote:

[quote=“yakman, post:16, topic:355639”]Oh you guys have the A* grade now…
coughgradeinflationcough[/quote]Not really, you need 60% to get a C and that increments by 10% each grade up to 80% (A). The A* grade gives the people who get over 80% overall and over 90% in A2 more recognition, and lets oxbridge set higher offers without requiring UMS marks.
